data.description: MAKE YOUR DREAM HOME COME TRUE with this move-in ready home in the quiet neighborhood of Raven Glen, a suburban retreat within the city limits of Ocala. This 3BR/2Bath and 2-car garage home is conveniently located within short driving distance to downtown Ocala, shopping centers, restaurants, hospitals and other amenities. This charming Holiday Builders built home features open concept living room, kitchen, breakfast bar and dining area. Its cathedral ceiling is accentuated with finely designed crown moldings. Wood-like tile flooring in living areas and carpet in bedrooms.. Master bedroom features a walk-in closet and a Master bath with a soaking tub, separate shower, double sink vanity and toilet. ENJOY your coffee in the mornings or glass of wine or bottle of beer on late afternoons at its bright and relaxing patio with wrap around glass and screened windows that can double as family room. It’s spacious privacy fenced backyard is perfect for outdoor activities or barbecue parties. Frontage of the home provides an expansive open space (WRA) and a panoramic view of the neighborhood. Nice curb appeal.
